    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a definitive example of high-revving naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system, both of which have been meticulously serviced to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. Power is managed by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential with a 3.62 final drive ratio. This chassis is structurally flawless, having received proactive subframe reinforcement and a full suspension refresh with poly-bushings and Bilstein dampers. The exterior finish is concours-ready, and the mechanical assembly is dry, tight, and free of any parasitic loss. A true turnkey masterpiece for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
